      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/bank-ceos-express-confidence-deals-consumer-finances-2024-11-13/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行首席执行官周三在纽约举行的行业会议上表达了对交易前景和美国消费者财务健康状况的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/bank-ceos-express-confidence-deals-consumer-finances-2024-11-13/</guid>
